phrases: Geniuses are valuable because they help make the world more peaceful.
I will not let them fall into the hands of evil!
In the name of the moon, Sailor Moon will punish you.

I am Usagi Tsukino, 14 years old.
I am clumsier than others and a bit of a crybaby.
One day, a strange black cat, Luna, appeared
and gave me a peculiar transforming brooch and made me a sailor warrior.
But, she wants me to fight against bad guys.
Oh well, I guess everything will be okay.
Is the Genius Girl a Monster?
Right now, the children of Japan are forced to study day after day
I have heard that there are more and more mothers
who are called academic moms who push their children mercilessly.
The parents are desperate to send their children
to the best kindergarten, the best primary school,
the best junior high school, the best high school
What about after graduating from the best college?
I will leave it to you.
I will leave it to you.
This is no time to be laughing.
How did you do on that mock exam?
The results are coming out tomorrow.
Usagi, I will not ask for the impossible.
But please, just do not fail.
No matter what, if there is a kid in first place,
there is always a kid in last place too!
It is not fair to yell at that kid just because her grades are bad!
You do not study, but you are always ready with an excuse.
I am the one who wants to cry!
It is about time you started studying.
Obviously, you do not care about me.
It must be nice to be a cat.
Oh, I wish I could be a cat.
Maybe, you do not know, but I have got lots to do,
Oh, you are reading a comic book!
I wish you would put more effort into finding the princess too.
Find the princess and fight against the enemy.
That is your fate and you cannot escape it.
You cannot do this to me!
Besides, who is this enemy anyway?
Something very evil that is not human.
I do not really get it.
To be honest, I do not really know who they are either.
Please try the Sailor V game.
Please try the Sailor V game.
My secret password is The rabbit on the moon makes rice cakes.
The moon rice cakes are sticky.
When I grilled them, they puffed up.
I still have no clue where she is.
Sailor Moon is not as dependable as I thought she would be.
I understand; do not grumble so.
By the way, I sensed a new and strange energy.
It could be another monster sent by our enemy.
It is Ami Mizuno from Class 5 again!
As expected, Ami Mizuno's at the top of our class.
Not only that, she is the best in the country!
Wow, she really is a genius.
By the way, do not pop up suddenly from such weird places!
I heard she attends Crystal Cram School.
Hey, that is the new place they just built, right?
My mom told me that it is really expensive.
I heard that Miss Mizuno's mom is a doctor.
However, she is on a scholarship, so she is attending for free!
But she is got a bad attitude.
It is like she thinks she is better than everybody else.
Oh, I cannot stand people like that.
It is such a nice day!
It is such a nice day!
But, it must be nice to be so smart.
I always have to worry that Mom's going to kill me.
It is about time you started going to a cram school!
It is about time you started going to a cram school!
It is about time you started going to a cram school!
I sense a strange energy coming from this girl.
If only we did not live in a high-rise apartment,
I could get a nice cat too.
Since she came from the sky, I thought she was an angel.
She is sweeter than I thought.
You are Miss Ami Mizuno from Class 5, right?
I am Usagi Tsukino from Class 1. Nice to meet you.
You are the first to know that right away!
If I become friends with her, I can get her to help me study for exams.
She could be a monster sent by the enemy.
By the way, Miss Mizuno, do you play games?
No, I have never tried before.
I will teach you how to play.
And in exchange, when tests come up...
I think you are thinking too much.
Obviously, something is wrong with me today.
Miss Mizuno, do you want to try?
This game really is pretty hard.
So, you would be doing good if you can score 500 points on your first try.
Wow, she got the highest score.
I did not know you were here.
There goes my help on exams...
I am sorry, Miss Tsukino, I have to go to cram school!
No, I am the one who should apologize.
I did not know you had cram school today.
I do not have any talents other than studying.
I feel like we live in completely different worlds.
I think this belongs to your friend.
I will make sure she gets it!
Crystal Cram School Stupid human beings.
Keep studying and provide us with your brain energy.
I do not use it much anyway.
Use the Crystal Disk and study hard.
You are on a scholarship, so you must not be lazy.
I have high expectations of you.
I hate to say it, but that disk gives me a headache.
If you use our newly developed Crystal Disks,
even you can be a genius!
So, is this the Crystal Disk?
I am just going to return this disk.
Are you finally in the mood to study a little, dumpling head?
Why do you always show up at the weirdest times?!
By the way, was not that cat just talking?
It would be big trouble if he found out.
Oh, I was in a hurry and forgot to return this.
Usagi, let us go to the computer lab at school.
I want to check out that disk.
I will just warn you now.
I do not know how to use a computer.
Knowing how to use a computer is normal these days, Miss Usagi.
Offer the energy of your brain and knowledge to our great ruler,
Crystal Cram School I still cannot believe it.
Turn me into a doctor who works at a university hospital!
I heard someone is sick here!
Everyone, get away from the computers right now!
I am the monster of knowledge, Garoben!
This genius girl is going to sacrifice her brain energy
Which means Miss Mizuno is not a monster after all!
Geniuses are valuable because they help make the world more peaceful.
I will not let them fall into the hands of evil!
Sailor warrior of love and justice, Sailor Moon!
In the name of the moon, I will punish you.
Why do apples fall from trees?
If you do not know the answer, take this!
It is because the Earth has gravity!
If you cannot answer, this is what happens.
Give up your genius brain energy!
It is not absorbing her energy.
You did not use the Crystal Disk, did you?!
You should study on your own without using machines!
That strange energy was from a sailor warrior...
Then, I will just take your brain instead!
So, Ami is the second sailor warrior, Sailor Mercury.
Yes, you are the second sailor warrior, Sailor Mercury.
Sorry for mistaking you for a monster.
But it is reassuring to have you as one of us.
Especially when I need to get ready for tests.
Once again, I am glad to meet you.
Let us work together, so we can beat the bad guys!
I am glad I met you!
She is such a tough girl, I think I might not be able to keep up.
